org.bytedeco.numpy

Class PyArrayInterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.numpy.PyArrayInterface
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    @Properties(inherit=numpy.class)
public class PyArrayInterface
extends org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
    This is the form of the struct that's returned pointed by the PyCObject attribute of an array __array_struct__. See https://docs.scipy.org/doc/numpy/reference/arrays.interface.html for the full documentation.
